channel.title: Asis Zinkama - HOPE ! ( Future Bass of something like that :3 )
channel.description:
**HI ! IT'S ME , again ! :rofl:** - Actually, it's been nearly 4 months and I finally have a new track! I still don't know what the main genre in this track is, could it be FutureBass again? Anyway, hopefully everyone will listen and support it! And wish everyone a good isolation during the Coronavirus epidemic ! :grin: Link this track : https://soundcloud.com/d-zinkama/hope **( drop in : 1 : 00 )**
My soundcloud : https://soundcloud.com/d-zinkama/ **THANKS A LOT !** 4591 ![Theo & Kate|500x500](upload://8yNNHtZmdICGEu3M2ddHRyKlACp.jpeg)
